<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men zhēn chéng de gǎn xiè zhǔ 迦南690</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men zhēn chéng de gǎn xiè zhǔ yé sū, dài lǐng zhe wǒ men de jiǎo bù.
 suī rán guò qù duō cì dé zuì tiān fù, zhǔ yī rán shēn shǒu kàn gù.
 wǒ men bù míng bái de míng tiān, tā jǐ míng bái. méi yǒu zǒu guò de dào lù, tā dōu jì shù.
 tā shì wǒ men líng hún de dà mù zhě, tā měi shí měi kè wèi wǒ men kāi lù.
 gǎn xiè tiān fù, gǎn xiè zhǔ yé sū,
 gǎn xiè shèng líng yǐn dǎo wǒ men de jiǎo bù. xīn de shì jì wǒ men hái tóng lù.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>690</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>